auc_vals = foreach(wg1 = w_genes, .combine = "c") %dopar% {
  y1 = edat[,wg1]
  auc1 = auc(roc(y_true, y1, levels=c("mild", "severe"), direction = "<"))
  as.numeric(auc1)
}

summary(auc_vals)
##    Min. 1st Qu.  Median    Mean 3rd Qu.    Max. 
##  0.2387  0.4890  0.4966  0.4901  0.5010  0.7542
